<aside class="footer__legal-notice" aria-label="Legal cost notice" data-footer-animate="legal-notice">
	<p class="footer__legal-notice-label" aria-hidden="true">Legal Notice</p>
	<p class="footer__legal-notice-text">
		In personal injury and litigation matters, if your case is unsuccessful you may be liable for
		the other party's legal costs. See <a
			class="footer__legal-notice-link"
			href="https://www.irishstatutebook.ie/eli/2015/act/65/enacted/en/html#sec149"
			target="_blank"
			rel="noopener noreferrer">Section 149 of the Legal Services Regulation Act 2015</a
		>.
	</p>
</aside>

<style>
